Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}与车里的商人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}都觉得这才是艾薇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}在我们内心深处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}每个人都是演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}这不可思议的艾薇拉
