Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}艾薇拉 艾薇拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,需要多些锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 嗯 这是阿拉克萨的房子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉克萨 我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已经失联了很多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但也许你可以帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要鼓起查纳尔;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但我恐怕你不会在这里找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 也许会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道查纳尔;是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的妈妈 你只是在和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是马特奥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你是阿拉克萨的子孙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的祖父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 知道几分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是苏非亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这可能听起来很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的祖父把我送到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让艾琳娜公主自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 这意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艾薇拉护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈告诉我这个故事很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我记住了。跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去哪里 我实的验室
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,祝我好运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有些阴森恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但这是唯一的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,保持一切秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当使瑞奇、奎恩接管，\NWhen Queen Shuriki\Ntook over,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她禁止所有的魔法除了她自己的。\Nshe banned all magic\Nexcept her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有向导在艾薇拉？\NSo there are no wizards\Nin Avalor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不是了。\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的奶奶把我爷爷的东西都藏在这里了，\NMy grandma hid\Nall my grandpa's\Nthings down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的母亲从来没有想与它做任何事情。\Nbut my mother never wanted\Nanything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它坐在这里所有锁起来\NSo it sat here\Nall locked up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我找到它。\Nuntil I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在努力教自己 从我魔法以来。\NI've been trying to teach\Nmyself magic ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，现在让我想想。\NOkay, now let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要一些东西。\NI just need a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，坐在这里，苏菲亚。\NOkay, sit here, Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要召唤我爷爷的神兽;。\NWe're going to summon\Nmy grandpa's chanul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是神兽 到底是什么？\NWhat is a chanul exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一种精神动物。\NA spirit animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它就像一个指南，所有的神奇的东西在世界上\NIt's like a guide to\Nall the magical stuff\Nin the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看不到，像艾琳娜公主。\Nthat we can't see,\Nlike Princess Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我爷爷的使博尔谁想出来的\NIt was my grandpa's chanul\Nwho figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她在护身符，告诉他如何让她出去。\Nshe was in the amulet\Nand told him how\Nto get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始吧。\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的tamborita在哪里？\NNow where's my tamborita?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，这是我第一次尝试这个咒语，\NOkay, this is the first time\NI've tried this incantation,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，它可能不工作的第一个八或九次。\Nso it may not work for the first\Neight or nine times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许十。啊哈。\NMaybe ten. Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎我们的动物精神，阿拉克萨。\NAppear to us,\Nanimal spirit of Alacazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,显灵吧 阿拉克萨的召唤\N{\i1} Illuminara Alacazar wayohel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是好的。\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一个鼓槌.。I have another\Ndrumstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.65,0:24:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们再试一次。\NLet's try that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,显灵吧 阿拉克萨的召唤\N{\i1} Illuminara Alacazar wayohel!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.99,0:24:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？\N( gasps )\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.83,0:25:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.86,0:25:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是.\NI am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,来自灵魂世界的问候！\NGreetings from\Nthe spirit world!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.87,0:25:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗？\NHow ya doin' today?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神兽勇士啊，\NO mighty chanul,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你尊重我们的存在。\Nyou honor us\Nwith your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，我知道你很兴奋。\NHey, I know you're excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到它。\NI get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.11,0:25:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它不是每天你遇到一个精神动物，对吗？\NIt's not every day\Nyou meet a spirit animal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.78,0:25:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但你召唤的我，我在这里，\NBut you called me,\NI'm here,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们可以跳过所有的号角，\Nso we can skip\Nall the fanfare,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.88,0:25:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和它相处，好吗？\Nand get on with it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.82,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，强大的神兽。\NOf course, mighty chanul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.89,0:25:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你可以叫我依佐。\NOh, you can\Ncall me Zuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.52,0:25:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，当然，伟大的依佐。\NYes, of course,\Nmighty Zuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.39,0:25:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必给我任何东西。\NYou don't have to\Ncall me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.19,0:25:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，你是公主，要自由艾琳娜。\NSo, you're the princess\Nthat's gonna free Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样想。\NI guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那么好吧。\NAll right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等，这是你必须做的。\NNow here's what\Nyou gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.64,0:25:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等.我想我只想召唤你。\NWait. I thought I just\Nhad to summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，所以我可以告诉你如何把她弄出来。\NUh-huh, so I can tell you\Nhow to get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.41,0:25:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是精神引导者做的。\NThat's what\Nspirit guides do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.71,0:25:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们引导你。\NThey guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.55,0:25:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，你需要魔杖\NFirst, you're gonna\Nneed the wand
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把埃琳娜放在那里。\Nthat put Elena in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇、奎恩的魔杖？\NQueen Shuriki's wand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但她把它在她的口袋里。\NBut she keeps it\Nin her pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.72,0:26:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了。\NThat's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你会知道到底在哪里找到它。\NYou'll know exactly\Nwhere to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.99,0:26:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，一旦你有了魔杖，\NNow, once you've got the wand,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.19,0:26:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它周围的护身符\Nyou just wrap\Nthe amulet around it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.16,0:26:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让他们在艾薇拉冠。\Nand put 'em on\Nthe crown of Aziluna.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.20,0:26:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的王冠？- 艾薇拉。\N- The crown of who?\N- Aziluna.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.73,0:26:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个伟大的疗愈者，可以撤消任何咒语或诅咒。\NHe was a great healer who could\Nundo any spell or curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.60,0:26:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个古老的阿如比尔他雕像\NThere's an ancient Maruvian\Nstatue of him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.74,0:26:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在山上的路。\Nway up in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.41,0:26:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点像一个神奇的事故医院。\NIt's kinda like a hospital\Nfor magical mishaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.04,0:26:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道它是在哪里，或者如何到达那里，\NBut I don't know where it is,\Nor how to get there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.71,0:26:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,或如何我要偷使瑞奇的魔杖。\Nor how I'm going to steal\NShuriki's wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.38,0:26:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我们都采取一个大呼吸。\NOkay, let's all\Ntake a big breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.75,0:26:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,吸。出。好的。\NIn. Out. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.75,0:26:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我有一些精神动物的智慧为你。\NNow I've got some\Nspirit animal wisdom for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.86,0:26:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为你是一个\NJust because\Nyou're the one
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.03,0:26:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,并不意味着你是唯一的一个。\Ndoesn't mean you're\Nthe only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.36,0:26:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不应该有任何意义的现在。你会得到它。\NThat's not supposed to\Nmake any sense right now.\NYou'll get it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.97,0:26:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先，你得去得到那根魔杖，公主。\NBut first, you gotta\Ngo get that wand, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.64,0:26:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，今天是你的精神指南是一种乐趣。\NAll right, it's been a pleasure\Nbeing your spirit guide today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.64,0:26:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行安全。再见.\NSafe travels. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.81,0:26:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那有多大？！\NHow great was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.48,0:27:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的第一神兽！\NI summoned\Nmy first chanul!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起的.哇！\NSorry. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，很好的举动。我敢打赌你是个好舞者，不是吗？\NHey, nice move. I bet you're\Na good dancer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.92,0:27:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我如何得到她的魔杖。\NThat's how I'll\Nget her wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会和她跳舞。\NI'll dance with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.63,0:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那不工作。\NThat won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇禁止跳舞时，她被禁止的音乐。\NShuriki outlawed dancing\Nwhen she banned music.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.90,0:27:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈还教我的桑布罗卡，虽然。\NMy mom still taught me\Nthe sambarosa, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.93,0:27:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须回到宫殿。我们？\N- We have to go\Nback to the palace.\N- We?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.10,0:27:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼多：当农民跟着她进入丛林，\NARMANDO: And when the farmer\Nfollowed her into the jungle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.57,0:27:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她变成了一辆捷豹！\Nshe turned into\Na jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.24,0:27:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但真的，她是一个邪恶的巫婆\NBut really, she was\Na wicked witch
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谁接管了丛林。\Nwho had taken over\Nthe jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.91,0:27:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,农夫试图逃跑…\NThe farmer tried\Nto escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的王国拥有一系列迷人的农业，Our kingdom has\Na wide array of\Nenchanted agriculture,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.45,0:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,和生物，更不要说\Nand creatures,\Nnot to mention
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.86,0:27:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的飞行马。\Nour flying horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记交易魔法王国。\NForget trading\Nwith Enchancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.86,0:27:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该入侵它。\NWe should invade it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.53,0:27:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你，公主。\NHere you are,\Nprincess.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里一段时间，苏菲亚。\NYou were out there\Na while, Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.83,0:27:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,飞们豹唱我的歌。\NThe jaquins\Nsang me a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.50,0:27:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他们似乎不能停止这样做。\NYes, they can't seem\Nto stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.84,0:27:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，阿曼多在表演一个节目\NWell, Armando\Nis putting on a show
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对于其他的小宝贝如果你想加入他们的行列。\Nfor the other little darlings\Nif you want to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.94,0:28:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上，我希望学习Actually, I was hoping\Nto learn
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.94,0:28:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一个我听过的艾薇拉舞蹈。\None of the Avaloran\Ndances I've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.18,0:28:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,的桑布罗卡。、NThe sambarosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.01,0:28:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我害怕我不知道那个舞蹈。\NOh, I'm afraid\NI don't know that dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.48,0:28:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艾薇拉最有名的舞蹈。\NIt's the most famous\Ndance in Avalor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.89,0:28:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以教给她。\NI can teach it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.79,0:28:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你不会的，阿曼多。\NNo, you won't, Armando.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的茶，你的优雅？\NMore tea, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.79,0:28:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢？有什么不好的法律吗？\NWhy not? Is there some kind\Nof law against dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.80,0:28:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚，没有人会通过一项法律，反对跳舞。\NSofia, no one would\Npass a law against dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.97,0:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像通过一个法律反对乐趣。\NThat's like passing\Na law against fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.07,0:28:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，在艾微拉，我们 \NWell, in Avalor, we--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只在特别的场合跳舞，\NWe only dance on\Nspecial occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.74,0:28:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,像皇家访问。\Nlike royal visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.81,0:28:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我们将很乐意给你sambarosa。\NSo we will be happy to\Nshow you the sambarosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.91,0:28:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，你的优雅？\NRight, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.31,0:28:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们必须。\NIf we must.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.98,0:28:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去拿吉他吧。\NLet me fetch the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大的.\NGreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.39,0:28:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的sambarosa舞蹈。\NThis is how you dance\Nthe sambarosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.02,0:28:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你加入的手，跺跺你的脚像这样。\NYou join hands\Nand stomp your feet like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.03,0:28:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来回移动，然后把你的伴侣。\NMove back and forth,\Nthen twirl your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.93,0:28:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！\NWhoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.10,0:28:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧。每个人都尝试！\NCome on.\NEveryone try!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.94,0:29:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,( both laughing )
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,( giggling )
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.91,0:29:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,( laughing )
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.41,0:29:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇、奎恩  能请你跳舞吗？\NQueen Shuriki,\Nwill you dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.68,0:29:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你是多么的可爱，\NOh, how sweet of you\Nto offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.75,0:29:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有太多的乐趣看你。\Nbut I'm having\Ntoo much fun watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.76,0:29:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信你的舞跳得比任何人都好。\NBut I'm sure you dance\Nbetter than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.89,0:29:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请？\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能对这样的一个亲爱的孩子说不呢？\NHow can I say no\Nto such a dear child?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.06,0:29:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NOw!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，你的优雅。我是如此笨拙。\NSo sorry, Your Grace.\NI'm so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.64,0:29:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,足够的跳舞！Enough dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.38,0:29:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.58,0:29:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是，如此令人愉快。\NI mean, so delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的必须回到我们的讨论，\NWe really must\Nget back to our discussions,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.75,0:29:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,国王和王后陛下。Your Majesties.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.32,0:29:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以玩捉迷藏？\NCan we play\Nhide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.06,0:29:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，是的，是的。无论你想要什么，亲爱的。\NYes, yes, yes.\NWhatever you want, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.16,0:30:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在可以处理了，埃斯特班。\NWe can dispose of that\Nnow, Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.00,0:30:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚，我不想玩捉迷藏。\NSofia, I don't wanna play\Nhide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.83,0:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这会很有趣，安伯。\NIt'll be fun, Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.43,0:30:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们躲着你找，阿曼多先生，好吗？\NIs it okay if we hide\Nand you seek, Mr. Armando?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.60,0:30:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，当然。那将是令人愉快的。\NOh, of course.\NThat would be\Ndelightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.91,0:30:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可以.一，二，三，四…\NOkay. One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.01,0:30:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧。\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.08,0:30:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,五，六，七，八…\NFive, six, seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.12,0:30:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,( counting continues )
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么，苏菲亚？\NWhat are you\Nup to, Sofia?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.02,0:30:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我稍后会解释，\NI'll explain later,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.52,0:30:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要你都隐藏，只要你能。\Nbut I need you both to hide\Nas long as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.36,0:30:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它是重要的。\NIt's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.83,0:30:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你得到它，苏菲亚，你为什么不告诉我们？\N- You got it, Sof.\N- Why won't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.03,0:30:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了你们的好，相信我。\NIt's for your own\Ngood, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.03,0:30:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.81,0:30:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了它!\NI got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，苏菲亚！\NRight on, Sofia!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.62,0:30:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么拉下来的。\NI don't know how\Nyou pulled that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:30:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇从来不让任何人接近她。\NShuriki never lets anyone\Nget close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.72,0:31:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看着她。\NLook at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.32,0:31:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩看起来像糖一样甜，但她有一些技能。\NGirl looks sweet as sugar,\Nbut she's got some skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.06,0:31:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，马泰奥，让我们去警笛拉的路上。\NOkay, Mateo, show us the way\Nto Aziluna.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个公主免费。\NWe've got a princess\Nto free.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.89,0:31:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚：那是什么？\NSOFIA: What's that?SOFIA: What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.19,0:31:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一个老阿如比尔寺。\NAn old Maruvian temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.09,0:31:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雕像在里面。\NThe statue is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.40,0:31:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，伙计，他们真的让去的地方。\NWhoa, man, they really\Nlet the place go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿如比尔消失了几个世纪前的。\NThe Maruvians vanished\Ncenturies ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.70,0:31:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人知道他们发生了什么，或者他们去了哪里。\NNo one knows what\Nhappened to them\Nor where they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.11,0:31:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所留下的古文明遗址的丸这样。\NAll that's left of\Nthe ancient civilization\Nof Maru are ruins like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.29,0:32:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚；雕像在哪里？\NSOFIA:\NWhere's the statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.26,0:32:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，传说有它\NWell, legend has it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要在迷人的水域游泳\Nyou need to swim across\Nthe enchanted waters
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.96,0:32:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为神奇的工作。\Nfor the magic to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.23,0:32:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的，苏菲亚。祝你好运.\NYou'll be fine, Sofia.\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.10,0:32:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可以.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.97,0:32:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,( grunting )
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.11,0:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个美人鱼会真的很方便\NBeing a mermaid would\Nreally come in handy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的权利。right about now.\N( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！你见过那个吗？\NWhoa! Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.49,0:32:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我能很容易地改变。\NI wish I could\Nshape shift that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.31,0:33:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定是它。\N( gasps )\NThat must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.14,0:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的.我要把护身符和魔杖\NRight. I have to put\Nthe amulet and wand
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.84,0:33:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在Aziluna冠。\Non the crown of Aziluna.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.99,0:33:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.88,0:34:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.55,0:34:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的护身符。\NMy amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.38,0:34:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它改变了颜色。\NIt changed color.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.15,0:34:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主吗？\NPrincess Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.34,0:34:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自由的！\NI'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.34,0:34:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于自由了！哇！\NI'm finally free!\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.28,0:34:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吗？-我很好。\N- Are you okay?\N- I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.84,0:34:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好。我想这就是发生的事情\NI'm good.\NI guess that's what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.05,0:34:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当你被困在一个护身符41年。\Nwhen you're stuck inside\Nan amulet for 41 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.92,0:34:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了怎么走了。\NYou forget how to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.25,0:34:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是我的唯一！\NI knew you were the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.79,0:34:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是...欢迎。\NYou're... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.06,0:34:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主！\NPrincess Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.63,0:35:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 杰特斯\NOh, jaquins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.43,0:35:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜公主。\NPrincess Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.60,0:35:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜公主。\NPrincess Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.03,0:35:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,( nervous giggle )
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.17,0:35:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是马特奥。\NI'm Mateo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉克萨的孙子。\NAlacazar's grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.57,0:35:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你不必低头，马特奥。\NOh, you don't have to bow,\NMateo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.47,0:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以叫我艾琳娜。\NAnd you can just\Ncall me Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，艾琳娜。\NOkay, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.74,0:35:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信你真的回来了。\NI can't believe\Nyou're really back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.41,0:35:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不能。\NNeither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.05,0:35:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这么长的护身符，\NI was in the amulet so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.55,0:35:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我可能永远不会离开。\NI thought I might\Nnever get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.58,0:35:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我在这里。\NBut here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很怪异¶ It feels so weird ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.59,0:35:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的脚放在地上\N¶ Having my feet\Non the ground ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.56,0:35:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有一段时间了，因为我一直走着\N¶ It's been a while since\NI've been walking around ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.33,0:35:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,用我自己的眼睛，我可以再次看到\N¶ With my own eyes,\NI can once again see ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.93,0:35:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的梦想已经实现了。\N¶ My dream has come true ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.57,0:35:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是自由的\N¶ I am free ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.78,0:35:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在，我在这里，有一个任务在手\N¶ But now that I'm here,\Nthere's a mission at hand ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.45,0:35:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们美丽的土地上驾驶\N¶ To drive that witch\Nout of our beautiful land ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.48,0:36:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要驱除黑暗带回光明\N¶ I'll banish the darkness\Nand bring back the light ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.85,0:36:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这段时间\N¶ 'Cause this time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.32,0:36:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备战斗\N¶ I'm ready to fight ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.33,0:36:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的时间\N¶ This is my time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.53,0:36:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间面对我的老敌人\N¶ My time to face\Nmy old foe ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.64,0:36:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间\N¶ My time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.84,0:36:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,收回我们很久以前的东西\N¶ Reclaim what was ours\Nlong ago ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.44,0:36:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的时间\N¶ This is my time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.68,0:36:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为了荣誉和骄傲而站起来\N¶ To stand up\Nwith honor and pride ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.52,0:36:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间\N¶ My time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.35,0:36:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经走得太远了\N¶ I've come too far ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.05,0:36:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被拒绝\N¶ To be denied ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.63,0:36:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我必须再一次飞到宫殿里去了\N¶ Now off I must fly\Nto the palace once more ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.20,0:36:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,赢回所有艾微拉的自由\N¶ To win back the freedom\Nof all Avalor ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生都在等待这一天\N¶ I've spent my whole life\Nwaiting just for this day ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.87,0:36:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不会在我的路上\N¶ And nothing will\Nget in my way ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.38,0:37:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的时间\N¶ This is my time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.32,0:37:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个不能失败的计划\N¶ I have a plan\Nthat can't fail ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.02,0:37:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间\N¶ My time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.16,0:37:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会使瑞奇我获胜\N¶ I won't stop\Ntill I prevail ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.49,0:37:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间\N¶ My time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.90,0:37:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为了纪念我的家人和朋友\N¶ To honor\Nmy family and friends ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.43,0:37:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的时间\N¶ My time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这再次是我的时间\N¶ This is my time\Nonce again ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.41,0:37:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的时间\N¶ This is my time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.75,0:37:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次\N¶ Once again ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.90,0:37:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我会在城市里看到你。\NOkay, I'll see you\Nback in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.70,0:37:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您去哪儿？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.90,0:37:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,给使瑞奇品尝自己的魔术。\NTo give Shuriki\Na taste of her own magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.80,0:37:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但使瑞奇、奎恩真的非常强大。\NBut Queen Shuriki\Nis really powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.44,0:38:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是没有她的魔杖。\NNot without her wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.91,0:38:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等等.我会和你一起去。\NWait. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.64,0:38:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样。\N- Me, too.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.44,0:38:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你已经为我冒了这么大的危险。\NNo. You've already\Nrisked so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.15,0:38:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我必须独自做的事情。\NThis is something\NI have to do alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.98,0:38:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.49,0:38:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须帮助她。走吧.\NWe've got to help her.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的.去月神。抓住公主。\NRight. Go, Luna.\NCatch that princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,露娜：让我们这样做！\NLUNA: Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子在哪里？\NWhere are those children?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.23,0:38:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,出来，出来，无论你在哪里。\NCome out, come out,\Nwherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.73,0:38:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们任何人。\NAny of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.64,0:38:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托.\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.58,0:38:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我和你一起去吗？\NYou want me\Nto go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.68,0:38:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，但我有这个。\NThanks, but I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.96,0:38:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,贸易协议已经准备好了\NThe trade agreement\Nis ready
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.99,0:38:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你的签名，你的优雅。\Nfor your signature,\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:38:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,完成.现在，这是照顾…\NDone. Now that\Nthat's taken care of...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜；使瑞奇\NELENA: Shuriki!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.13,0:39:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？-嗯？\N- Huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.81,0:39:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜公主！\NPrincess Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.11,0:39:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是来为你的罪行买单的时候了。\NThe time has come\Nto pay for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.68,0:39:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,犯罪了吗？犯了什么罪？\NCrimes?\NWhat crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.65,0:39:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇入侵艾微拉，\NShuriki invaded Avalor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.28,0:39:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,推翻王室。\Nand overthrew\Nthe royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.38,0:39:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的家人。\NMy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗？\NIs this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.55,0:39:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，艾琳娜。\NOh, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.95,0:39:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有些继承他们的王国。\NSome inherit\Ntheir kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.86,0:39:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人必须采取他们的力量。\NOthers have to take\Ntheirs by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.39,0:39:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.69,0:39:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我在这里带我的回来。\NThen I'm here\Nto take mine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但没有你艾微拉已经好多了没有你。\NBut Avalor has been\Nso much better without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.57,0:39:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要毁了一件好事呢？\NWhy ruin a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.57,0:39:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找这个？\NLooking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.31,0:39:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么弄到的？\NHow did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.01,0:39:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个小公主。\NIt was that little princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.54,0:39:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,项链的那个。\NThe one with\Nthe necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.88,0:39:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等等.苏菲亚参与了？\NWait. Sofia's\Ninvolved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.31,0:39:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对.她把我从她的护身符，\NYes. She freed me\Nfrom her amulet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.48,0:39:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以自由avalor从你。\Nso that I could free Avalor\Nfrom you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.59,0:39:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我不知道。\NOh, I don't know\Nabout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.25,0:39:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它需要更多的不是魔杖让你一个女巫\NIt takes more than\Na wand to make you\Na sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.26,0:40:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的咒语回荡在我的脑海里40年了，使瑞奇。\NYour spell has echoed in my mind\Nfor 40 years, Shuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.06,0:40:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道它的心。\N know it by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.86,0:40:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧\N{\i1} Vadisima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,( evil laugh )
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.93,0:40:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须做得比这更好。\NYou'll have to do\Nbetter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.20,0:40:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧\N{\i1} Vadisima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.78,0:40:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.41,0:40:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.25,0:40:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没有见过这幅画。\NI've never seen\Nthis painting before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.79,0:40:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，那不是普通的画，艾琳娜。\NOh, that's no\Nordinary painting, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.79,0:40:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是阿拉克萨保护你的小妹妹和祖父母\NThat's how Alacazar\Nprotected your little\Nsister and grandparents--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.43,0:40:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个被施了魔法的绘画里，即使我的魔法无法触及。\Ninside an enchanted painting\Neven my magic cannot touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.20,0:40:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Abuelo. Abuela.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.60,0:40:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔。\NIsabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.37,0:40:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说到家庭，\NAnd speaking of family,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有向你的表弟埃斯特班打招呼。you haven't said hello to\Nyour cousin Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,( nervous stammer )
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.71,0:40:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.28,0:40:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能是埃斯特班。This cannot be Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.21,0:40:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你被困在一个护身符长时间的。\NYou were stuck in\Nthat amulet a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.28,0:40:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能仍然是16，但埃斯特班长大了。\NYou may still be 16,\Nbut Esteban grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.05,0:41:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等等.你和她在一起？\NWait. You're with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.75,0:41:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我. ..我别无选择，艾琳娜。\NI... I had\Nno choice, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的，埃斯特班？( laughs )\NIs that so, Esteban?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.56,0:41:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,给我消失、N{\i1} Vadisima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.63,0:41:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住她！\NSeize her!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.74,0:41:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,( panting )
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了！\NFound ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.51,0:41:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，发生什么事了？\NUh, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.85,0:41:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有，阿曼多。\NNothing, Armando.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.68,0:41:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是把事情恢复的顺序。\NI'm just setting things\Nback in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.85,0:41:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，别这么快，使瑞奇！\NHey, not so fast, Shuriki!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.02,0:41:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.02,0:41:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,跳上来，艾琳娜。\NHop on, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.32,0:41:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不，等等。不要离开，斯凯拉。No, wait.\NDon't leave, Skylar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.42,0:41:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Vadisima，守卫，阻止他们！\N{\i1} Vadisima! {\i}\NGuards, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.46,0:41:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她被黄昏。\NI want her captured\Nby nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她和那个小公主。\NHer and that\Nlittle princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.93,0:41:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,离开索菲亚 离开这。\NLeave Sofia out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.70,0:41:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当你在它的时候把他们锁起来。\NAnd lock them up\Nwhile you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.20,0:41:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,米兰达：把你的手从我身上拿开！\NMIRANDA: Get your hands\Noff me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.94,0:41:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会后悔的。\NYou'll regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.44,0:41:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信。\NI doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.67,0:41:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\NWait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.44,0:41:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,斯凯拉，我们要回去。\NSkylar, we have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.21,0:41:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？那么她能把你关了吗？\NWhy? So she can\Nfinish you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.21,0:41:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你是勇敢的，公主，\NYou are brave, princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.85,0:42:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的战斗战略，不那么好。\Nbut your battle strategy,\Nnot so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.78,0:42:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜，发生了什么事？\NElena, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.85,0:42:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了，苏菲亚，\NI tried my best, Sofia,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.89,0:42:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能得到拼写正确，\Nbut I couldn't\Nget the spell right,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇家人现在。\Nand Shuriki\Nhas your family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.96,0:42:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她有我的家人？\NShe has my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.69,0:42:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉。\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.49,0:42:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那里。弓箭手，锁定你的箭。\NThere she is.\NArchers, lock your arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.83,0:42:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,画！\NDraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.73,0:42:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哇。他们是射箭！\NWhoa. They're\Nshooting arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.83,0:42:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回避动作。躲避和编织。\NEvasive action.\NDodge and weave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.97,0:42:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们可以这样做。\NYeah, we could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.54,0:42:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我们可以打出去。\NOr we could just\Nget on up outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.14,0:42:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们可以去我的地方。-大。坚持.\N- We can go to my place.\N- Great. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.76,0:42:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我希望他们没事。\NOh, I hope they're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.27,0:42:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好，罗伦。苏菲亚在哪里？\NThis is not okay, Roland.\NWhere is Sofia?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.27,0:42:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让我们离开这里，苏菲亚，我们会发现Sofia。\NI will get us\Nout of here, Miranda,\Nand we will find Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.74,0:43:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,囚犯们被固定了，议长埃斯特班。\NThe prisoners are secured,\NChancellor Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.34,0:43:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那些囚犯是皇室，\NThose prisoners are royalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.61,0:43:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会这样对待他们。\Nand you will\Ntreat them as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.21,0:43:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，财政大臣。\NYes, chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.01,0:43:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是彝族。然而另一个混乱清理。\NAy yi yi.\NYet another mess to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.62,0:43:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以埃琳娜公主的生活。\NSo Princess Elena lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.89,0:43:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然。\NApparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.02,0:43:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她是王位的合法继承人。\NShe is the rightful\Nheir to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.69,0:43:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该帮助她。\NWe should be\Nhelping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.13,0:43:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你建议我们做什么，嗯？\NWhat do you suggest\N{\i1}we{\i} do, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.19,0:43:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,打女王？因为我们会输。Fight the queen?\NBecause we will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.86,0:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的表弟，史蒂芬。\NBut Elena's\Nyour cousin, Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.87,0:43:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她的祖父母抚养我像一个儿子。\NAnd her grandparents\Nraised me like a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.80,0:43:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在想他们所发生的事情。\NAnd I think about\Nwhat happened to them\Nevery day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.20,0:43:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不需要你提醒我，阿曼多。\NSo I do not need you\Nto remind me, Armando.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.13,0:43:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜，发生了什么事？\NElena, what happened\Nback there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.27,0:44:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来不知道发生了什么事\NI never knew\Nwhat happened
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.47,0:44:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,直到今天我的姐姐和我的祖父母。\Nto my sister\Nand my grandparents\Nuntil today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.57,0:44:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看到他们被困在那幅画里\NSeeing them trapped\Nin that painting
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了我最后一次见到伊莎贝尔的时候。\Nreminded me of\Nthe last time I saw Isabel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.68,0:44:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔？-我的小妹妹。- Isabel?\N- My little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.15,0:44:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她整天都在花园里，\NShe'd been out in\Nthe garden all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.85,0:44:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为jaquins建设新机。\Nbuilding a new feeder\Nfor the jaquins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.82,0:44:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她是肮脏的，\NShe was filthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.86,0:44:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的父母在回家的路上吃晚饭，\Nand our parents were\Non their way home for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.99,0:44:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我让她改变。\Nso I asked her to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.83,0:44:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿着一件干净的衣服回来了，And she comes back\Nwearing a clean dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.93,0:44:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但她的手和脸仍然覆盖在泥土中。but her hands and face\Nare still covered in dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.13,0:44:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚打扫完她\NI had just finished\Ncleaning her off
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.00,0:44:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当我听到我们的父母的马车在外面拉。\Nwhen I heard our parents'\Ncarriage pull up outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.27,0:44:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然后，使瑞奇到达。\NAnd then,\NShuriki arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.68,0:44:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉；I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,当我看见她在那迷人的画今天，\NWhen I saw her in\Nthat enchanted painting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.65,0:44:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她仍然在她脸上涂抹。\Nshe still had\Na smudge on her cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.88,0:44:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我错过了一个点。\NI guess I missed a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.78,0:44:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,( door creaking )
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.22,0:44:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有可以把他们弄出来的咒语。\NWe have the spell\Nthat can get them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.66,0:44:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做什么？-我们。\N- We do?\N- We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.02,0:45:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖父给我看它在哪里\NYour grandfather\Nshowed me where it was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.39,0:45:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在他离开之前，但我从未学过魔法，\Nbefore he left,\Nbut I never learned magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.36,0:45:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不能施展法术。\Nso I cannot\Ncast the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.17,0:45:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做的，马泰奥。\NYou will have\Nto do it, Mateo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.07,0:45:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，呃，为什么我能这样做呢？\NAnd, uh, why would I\Nbe able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.87,0:45:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,马泰奥，你在那边的地下室\NMateo, you're down there\Nin the basement
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.37,0:45:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,练习魔法的白天和黑夜。\Npracticing magic\Nday and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.54,0:45:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我不知道吗？\NYou think\NI don't know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.91,0:45:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但埃琳娜，我必须警告你。\NBut Elena,\NI must warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.14,0:45:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们带来了使瑞奇仍然掌权To bring them out\Nwith Shuriki still in power
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.35,0:45:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,将使他们处于巨大的危险之中。\Nwill put them\Nin great danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.35,0:45:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- ( horses approaching )\N- ( knocking )
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.99,0:45:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有客人。快速，隐藏，在那里。\NWe have visitors.\NQuick, hide, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.02,0:45:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以.来了，来了。\N- ( knocking )\N- Okay. Coming, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.83,0:45:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拉法，你听到了吗？\NRafa, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.93,0:45:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说埃琳娜公主已经回来了。\NThey're saying that\NPrincess Elena has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.53,0:45:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，快点。快点。进来。\NOh, hurry.\NHurry. Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须小心。\NWe have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.57,0:45:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主，没关系。\NPrincess Elena,\Nit's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.51,0:45:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以信任他们。We can trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.01,0:45:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的。\NIt is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.18,0:45:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,公主的生活！\NThe princess lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.05,0:45:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的公主。\NMy princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.12,0:45:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必鞠躬。\NYou don't have to bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.09,0:46:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，好吗。\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.59,0:46:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在你的指挥下。\NWe are at your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.12,0:46:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我会自己承担使瑞奇。\NI will take on\NShuriki myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.79,0:46:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们，你们所有人，\NThank you,\Nall of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.69,0:46:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是我的战斗，不是你的。\Nbut this is my fight,\Nnot yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.06,0:46:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那个必须面对她的人。\NI'm the one\Nwho must face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.80,0:46:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能是唯一的一个，但你不是唯一的一个。\NYou may be the one,\Nbut you're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.80,0:46:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,依佐说，现在我知道他是什么意思。\NZuzo said that, and now\NI know what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.64,0:46:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以.他是什么意思？\NOkay. What did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都可以帮助。你不需要独自面对Shuriki。\NWe can all help.\NYou don't need\Nto face Shuriki alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.94,0:46:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要告诉我们该做什么。\NYou just need to tell us\Nwhat to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.25,0:46:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，你知道，所有这一切的时候\NHmm. You know,\Nall this time
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.08,0:46:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困在了护身符，我想我是孤独的，\NI was stuck in the amulet,\NI thought I was alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.78,0:46:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是对的，苏菲亚。它不必是这样。\Nbut you're right, Sofia.\NIt doesn't have to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我都有你。\NI have all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.99,0:46:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，可是什么样的我们对使瑞奇和她所有的士兵吗？\NYeah, but what good\Nare we against Shuriki\Nand all her soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.06,0:46:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在盘算着，\NI'm still\Nfiguring that out,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.56,0:46:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要每个人的帮助。\Nbut I'm going to need\Neveryone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.76,0:46:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和你在一起。-所有的方式。\N- We're with you.\N- All the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.60,0:46:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你。\NNot just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.97,0:46:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人。\NEveryone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.03,0:47:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪儿？Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.83,0:47:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,宫殿的秘密入口。\NA secret back entrance\Nto the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.13,0:47:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我曾经偷偷溜出去时，我不应该。\NNot that I ever snuck out\Nwhen I wasn't supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.35,0:47:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在交会点见你，斯凯拉。\NI'll see you at\Nthe rendezvous point, Skylar.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.31,0:47:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好。\NYou better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.95,0:47:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们如何找到我的家人？\NHow will we find\Nmy family?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.32,0:47:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个地方使瑞奇会把他们。\NThere's only one place\NShuriki would've put them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.39,0:47:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主吗？！\NPrincess Elena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.63,0:47:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿。你看起来像个好人\NHey there.\NYou look like a nice guy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.63,0:47:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谁只想做正确的事。\Nwho just wants to do\Nthe right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.53,0:47:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？我的意思是，我。I do?\NI mean, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.03,0:47:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你需要什么，公主。\NWhatever you need,\Nprincess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.70,0:47:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你的服务。\NI am at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.68,0:48:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈。请原谅我,\NAhem. Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.21,0:48:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但使瑞奇、奎恩希望你们两\Nbut Queen Shuriki\Nwants the both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.71,0:48:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,马上向她报告。to report to her\Nright away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.35,0:48:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去的。你呆在这里。\NI'll go.\NYou stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.25,0:48:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，但她要求看到你们俩。No, but she asked\Nto see the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.92,0:48:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中的一个必须看囚犯。\NOne of us has to\Nwatch the prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.72,0:48:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，等待。坚持。\NUm, wait.\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.76,0:48:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害。\NThat hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.59,0:48:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，有一个警卫不会离开。Oh, one of the guards\Nwouldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.26,0:48:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚，如果你退缩了，\NSofia, if you shrank down,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.40,0:48:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以偷偷的过去那个警卫。\Nyou could sneak\Nright past that guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.90,0:48:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不是我的护身符了。\NBut you're not\Nin my amulet anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.60,0:48:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我还有我的权力吗？\NDo you think I still\Nhave my powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.37,0:48:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一种方法可以找到。\NThere's only one way\Nto find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.41,0:48:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我是小的。\NI wish I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.38,0:48:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,( yells )
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.08,0:48:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼多，我需要你分散我的注意力。\NArmando, I need you\Nto distract the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.08,0:48:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.请原谅我.你好.\NHello. Excuse me.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.45,0:48:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是什么？What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.29,0:48:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些非常，非常重要\NThere's something\Nvery, very important
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.89,0:48:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须告诉你。在这里.\NI must tell you.\NOver here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.10,0:49:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望再次大。\NI wish to be big again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.27,0:49:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.所有：苏菲亚！\N- Hi.\N- ALL: Sofia!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.41,0:49:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘我们要快点。\NSh. We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.64,0:49:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你有很多解释要做。\NYou have a lot\Nof explaining to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.08,0:49:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈，我会的…后来。我的承诺。Mom, I will... later.\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.81,0:49:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在，我们必须找到一种方法来获得过去的后卫。\NBut right now, we have to find\Na way to get past that guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.82,0:49:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会照顾他。\NI'll take care\Nof him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.09,0:49:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当农夫跟着她进入丛林，\NAnd when the farmer\Nfollowed her into the jungle,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.55,0:49:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她变成了一辆捷豹！\Nshe turned into\Na jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你必须告诉我的重要的事情吗？\NThis is the important thing\Nyou had to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.29,0:49:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有听到结局。\NYou haven't heard\Nthe ending yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.26,0:49:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住他！\NGrab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.23,0:49:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了他！\NGot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.83,0:49:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好.\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.24,0:49:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，这是艾琳娜公主。\NDad, this is\NPrincess Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.58,0:49:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我把你的家人给我的危险。\NI'm sorry for the danger\NI put your family in.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.31,0:49:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已经等了这么多年\NBut I've waited\Nso many years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.18,0:49:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能我的护身符的人自由的公主，\Nfor the one princess that could\Nfree me from the amulet,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.08,0:49:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是苏菲亚。\Nand that was Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.99,0:49:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,从第一天开始，我就感觉到她搬进了你的城堡。\NI sensed it from\Nthe very first day\Nshe moved into your castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.79,0:49:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以当我挑选了苏菲亚的欢迎礼物，\NSo when I was picking out\NSofia's welcome gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.03,0:50:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让它发光？\Nit was you who made\Nthe amulet glow?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.03,0:50:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对.我需要一个年轻的足够的人\NYes. I needed someone\Nyoung enough
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.26,0:50:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接近使瑞奇没有使她怀疑，\Nto get close to Shuriki\Nwithout making her suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.27,0:50:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但勇敢和聪明，让我出去。but brave and clever enough\Nto get me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.63,0:50:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不应该对她生气。\NSo you shouldn't be\Nmad at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.37,0:50:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该自豪。\NYou should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.37,0:50:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚，你还是应该告诉我们发生了什么。\NSofia, you still should've\Ntold us what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.54,0:50:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道.我只是想让你所有的麻烦。\NI know. I just wanted to\Nkeep you all out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.44,0:50:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，那太晚了。\NWell, it's\Ntoo late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.21,0:50:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想可能是一次原谅。\NI think a pardon\Nmay be in order just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.05,0:50:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个计划让你们都安全，\NI have a plan to get you\Nall to safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.35,0:50:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们必须快点。\Nbut we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.12,0:50:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了我的耐心，埃斯特班。I'm losing my patience,\NEsteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.55,0:50:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜公主在哪里？\NWhere is Princess Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.36,0:50:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,使瑞奇、奎恩 当我帮助你入侵艾微拉，\NQueen Shuriki,\Nwhen I helped you invade Avalor,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.23,0:50:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应我，我的家庭里没有人会受到伤害。\Nyou promised me that no one\Nin my family would be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.66,0:50:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也答应你的力量，现在看看你，\NI also promised you power,\Nand look at you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.17,0:50:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,总理埃斯特班。\NChancellor Esteban.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.37,0:50:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是很高兴我保持了我的承诺之一，\NJust be happy I kept\None of my promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.87,0:50:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,否则你会像你的阿姨和叔叔一样。\Nor you'll wind up like\Nyour aunt and uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.74,0:50:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看到我，你的优雅。\NYou wanted to see me,\NYour Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.54,0:50:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想看到任何人直到那些公主发现。\NI don't want to see\Nanyone until those\Nprincesses are found.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.41,0:50:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，使瑞奇\NHey there, Shuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.42,0:50:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见.\NLong time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.35,0:51:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经把你的秃鹰之外，而不是在我的宫殿。\NI've put up with you buzzards\Noutside, but not in my palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.39,0:51:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这里很舒适。\NBut it's so comfy\Nin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.42,0:51:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，这是一个很好的小鲈鱼。\NOoh, here's a nice\Nlittle perch.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.49,0:51:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,离开我的王位。\NGet off my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.89,0:51:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让它消失 错过了我！\N-{\i1} Vadisima! {\i}\N- Missed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.90,0:51:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,捕捉那兽。\NCapture that beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.60,0:51:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到女王。移动！\NYou heard the queen.\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.83,0:51:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，先生。\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.87,0:51:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我们看看拼写。\NOkay, let's see the spell.Okay, let's see the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.08,0:51:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哇喔 这…波浪鼓…？\NWhoa.\N{\i1} Tlah...cui...lolli...?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.61,0:51:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，孩子，这是一个绕口令。\NOh, boy,\Nthat's a tongue twister.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.55,0:51:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜：马泰奥\NELENA: Mateo!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.72,0:51:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是你。\NOh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，伊莎贝尔！\NOh, Isabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须让他们出来，马泰奥。\NYou have to get them\Nout, Mateo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.02,0:51:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在。\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.59,0:51:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N( sighs )\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.89,0:51:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Tlahcuilolli apartad.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.46,0:51:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Tlahcuilolli apareced.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.36,0:51:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Tlahcuilolli vivid!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.14,0:51:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔！-艾琳娜！\N- Isabel!\N- Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.94,0:52:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是如此的想念你。\NI missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.28,0:52:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,让我只是…\NLet me just...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.15,0:52:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是安全的。\NYou're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.12,0:52:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,祖父，奶奶\N{\i1} Abuelo, abuela.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.99,0:52:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,祖父 宫殿看起来如此不同。\N{\i1} ABUELO:{\i} The palace looks\Nso different.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.92,0:52:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？-使瑞奇 她还在这里。\N- What happened to Shuriki?\N- She's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.79,0:52:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该让阿拉克萨把我们那幅画。\NI never should've let\NAlacazar put us in\Nthat painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.43,0:52:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我们以后能谈谈吗？\NUh, can we talk\Nabout this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.90,0:52:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须去。\NWe have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.30,0:52:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都匆匆忙忙。在jaquin。\NEveryone hurry.\NGet on a jaquin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.74,0:52:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，公主。\NWhoa, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.34,0:52:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该给我一个头。\NYou should've given me\Na head count.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.31,0:52:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中的一些人可能不得不加倍。\NSome of you may\Nhave to double up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.14,0:52:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这些jaquins会带家人回到你的船，These jaquins will take\Nyour family back to your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.25,0:52:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要带其他人。and we're taking\Nthe others.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.82,0:52:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始，人们骑jaquins？Since when do people\Nride jaquins?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.79,0:52:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要习惯它。\NDon't get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.69,0:52:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会离开使瑞奇了，艾琳娜。\NI'm not running away\Nfrom Shuriki again, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.99,0:52:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不跑奶奶你会看到。\NWe're not running\Naway,{\i1} abuela. {\i}\NYou'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.94,0:53:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要留下来帮助艾琳娜。\NI'm going to stay\Nand help Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.01,0:53:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？如果我知道，我会得到另一只鸟呢。\NWhat? If I knew that,\NI would've gotten on\Nanother bird thingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.01,0:53:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该帮助，太，罗妮。\NWe should help, too, Rollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.31,0:53:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算，但孩子们\NI intend to,\Nbut the children
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.35,0:53:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,应该回到它的安全的地方。\Nshould return to the ship\Nwhere it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.88,0:53:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会没事的，爸爸。\NWe'll be okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.35,0:53:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会孤单一人。每个人都来了。\NWe won't be alone.\NEveryone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.19,0:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伦：你的意思是什么，每个人？\NROLAND: What do you mean,\Neveryone?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,男人：来吧。我们要去城堡。\NMAN: Come on.\NWe're going to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.36,0:53:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,万岁艾微拉  所有万岁艾微拉\N- Viva Avalor!\N- ALL: Viva Avalor!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.50,0:53:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,( all chattering )
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.37,0:53:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，使瑞奇。\NHey, Shuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.04,0:53:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里有一点孤独。\NI'm getting a little\Nlonely up here. ( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.04,0:53:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又是你；消失吧You again.\N{\i1} Vadisima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.58,0:53:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了\N( screams )\NToo slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.01,0:53:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我消失\N-{\i1} Vadisima! {\i}\N- ( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.65,0:53:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次想念我。\NMissed me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.42,0:53:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要有比这更好的目标\NYou're gonna have to aim\Nbetter than that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.89,0:53:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要杀死我。\Nif you're gonna zap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.39,0:53:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我会的，你的害虫  消失吧\NOh, I will, you pest.\N{\i1} Vadisima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.66,0:53:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦.嗯。\NOh. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.53,0:53:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的射门，使瑞奇。\NNice shot, Shuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.06,0:53:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这是一个爆炸分散你的注意力，\NWell, it's been a blast\Ndistracting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.20,0:53:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要离开这里。-让我分心？\N- but I'm outta here.\N- Distracting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.20,0:54:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她在说什么，埃斯特班？\NWhat is she talking\Nabout, Esteban?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.17,0:54:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N- ( voices nearby )\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.00,0:54:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\NWhat is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了，陛下。\NThey're coming,\NYour Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.37,0:54:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来了？\NWho is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.44,0:54:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有艾微拉人民。\NAll of Avalor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.68,0:54:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,( people singing )
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.25,0:54:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…唱歌吗？\NIs that... singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.28,0:54:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,( singing continues )
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.86,0:54:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们将再次走向宫殿\N¶ So we will march\Nto the palace once more ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.86,0:54:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,给所有艾微拉自由\N¶ To bring back the freedom\Nof all Avalor ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.27,0:54:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经度过了我们的一生只为等待这一天\N¶ We've spent our whole lives\Nwaiting just for this day ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.53,0:54:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，没有，什么都没有\N¶ And nothing,\Nno, nothing ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.54,0:54:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,将站在我们的方式\N¶ Will stand in our way ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.38,0:54:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的时代¶ This is our time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.91,0:54:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一起作为一个，我们不会失败\N¶ Together as one,\Nwe won't fail ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.28,0:54:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时间\N¶ Our time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.82,0:54:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次，我们知道我们会获胜\N¶ This time we know\Nwe'll prevail ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.49,0:54:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时间\N¶ Our time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.46,0:55:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为了纪念我们的家人和朋友\N¶ To honor\Nour family and friends ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.60,0:55:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时间\N¶ Our time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.17,0:55:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的时代\N¶ This is our time ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.57,0:55:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再次\N¶ Once again ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.52,0:55:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,停止！-停在那里。\N- Halt!\N- Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.42,0:55:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会照顾他们的。\NI'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.62,0:55:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,支撑你自己，米兰达。\NBrace yourself, Miranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.49,0:55:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把大门锁上了。\NThey locked the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.29,0:55:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须打破它。\NWe'll have to break it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.80,0:55:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或者我们可以飞到另一边，打开它。\NOr we can fly around\Nthe other side and open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.20,0:55:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这也将工作。\NThat'll work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.80,0:56:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在一起。\NStay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.36,0:56:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,保持坚强！\NStay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.63,0:56:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫：立场坚定，男人。\NGUARD: Stand firm, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.50,0:56:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,以女王的名义停止。\NStop in the name\Nof the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.97,0:56:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.37,0:56:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止他们！\NStop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.64,0:56:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-有太多了-撤退！运行！\N- There's just too many.\N- Retreat! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.31,0:56:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我现在就去这里。\NI think I'll just\Ngo over here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.84,0:56:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,懦夫！足够的！\NCowards!\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.38,0:56:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,魔云\N{\i1} Obscuras!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.02,0:56:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,( thunder rumbling )
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.99,0:56:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,立即离开我的宫殿。\NLeave my palace\Nat once.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.59,0:56:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你的宫殿，使瑞奇。\NIt's not your palace,\NShuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.43,0:56:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的，你不能阻止我们所有人。\NIt's ours, and you can't\Nstop all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.56,0:56:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不必。\NI don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.66,0:56:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要阻止你。\NI only need\Nto stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.67,0:56:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯特班！\NEsteban!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.40,0:56:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.67,0:56:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜，接着。\NElena, catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.51,0:57:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈!你不能用魔杖在我身上，女孩。\NHa! You can't use the wand\Non me, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.95,0:57:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是这样，但让我们看看你是多么强大，没有它。\NMaybe so, but let's see\Nhow powerful you are without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.28,0:57:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的统治结束了，使瑞奇。\NShuriki, your reign\Nis over.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.65,0:57:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,( all gasping )
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.65,0:57:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.\N( sobbing )
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.63,0:57:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她走了，艾琳娜。我们赢了。\NShe's gone, Elena.\NWe won.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.74,0:58:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,经过这些年。\NAfter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.27,0:58:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所有艾微拉人们合法继承人，\NAll hail the rightful heir\Nof Avalor,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.44,0:58:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜公主\NPrincess Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.61,0:58:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,( people cheering )
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.75,0:58:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等.我现在负责这个王国？\NWait. I'm in charge\Nof the kingdom now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.78,0:58:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是老大。\NYou are the eldest child.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.52,0:58:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,王冠是你的。\NThe crown goes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.85,0:58:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？\NIt does?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.99,0:58:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会是伟大的统治者，艾琳娜。\NYou will be\Na great ruler, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.69,0:58:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你会有你的祖父和我\NAnd you'll have\Nyour grandfather and I
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.63,0:58:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为了帮助你，所以没有什么可以担心的。\Nto help you,\Nso there's nothing\Nto worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.50,0:58:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去和你的人民。\NNow go and address\Nyour people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.97,0:58:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的.称呼我的人。\NRight.\NAddress my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.80,0:58:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.20,0:58:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.你好.\NHello. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.77,0:58:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗？嘿\NHow are you?\NHey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.11,0:58:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你所做的一切。\NAnd thank you\Nfor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.35,0:58:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾琳娜，我猜这是属于你的。\NElena, I guess\Nthis belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.88,0:58:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚，我想让你拥有它，\NSofia, I want you\Nto have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.39,0:58:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为我对艾微拉所做的一切。\Nfor all you've done\Nfor Avalor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.39,0:58:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，我认为我已经看到足够的护身符\NBesides, I think I've\Nseen enough of that amulet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.72,0:58:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一辈子。\Nfor a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.79,0:58:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，艾琳娜。\NThank you, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.47,0:59:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，表弟。\NThank you, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.24,0:59:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿，我不知道你是谁在。\NFor a moment, I wasn't sure\Nwhose side you were on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.51,0:59:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是在我们身边，\NI was always\Non our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.21,0:59:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能使瑞奇找到一种方式来破坏那幅画。\Nbut I couldn't let\NShuriki find a way\Nto destroy that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.51,0:59:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的家人在那里。\NOur family was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.31,0:59:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，我假装跟着她\NAnd so, I pretended\Nto follow her
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.75,0:59:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保持他们的安全。\Nto keep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.92,0:59:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解，艾琳娜。\NI hope you understand, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.83,0:59:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜！-艾萨！\N- Elena!\N- Isa!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.93,1:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,任何时候你需要一个骑，公主，\NAny time you need\Na ride, princess,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.07,1:00:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的华金。I'm your jaquin.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.97,1:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我将每一个铃声让你..\NLet every bell\Nin Avalor ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.91,1:00:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是自由的！\NWe are free!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.78,1:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,( bells tolling )
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.05,1:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎么了？-伟大的。\N- How was that?\N- Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.46,1:00:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,苏菲亚；所有的王国和\NSOFIA:{\i1} "And all across{\i}\N{\i1} the kingdom,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.79,1:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾微及的人欢呼\N{\i1} the people of Avalor{\i}\N{\i1} cheered,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.93,1:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们失去了的公主终于回家了\N{\i1} for their lost princess{\i}\N{\i1} had finally come home.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.90,1:00:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,于是就开始了艾琳娜公主的统治，\NThus began the reign\Nof Princess Elena,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.80,1:00:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,并与它，一个新时代的喜悦和繁荣\Nand with it, a new age\Nof joy and prosperity
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.97,1:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的艾微拉。”\Nfor all of Avalor."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.84,1:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,精彩的.\NWonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.01,1:00:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会称这是一个非常快乐的结局。\NI would call that\Na very happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.81,1:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但我不认为她的故事已经结束了。\NIt is, but I don't think\Nher story is over just yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.95,1:00:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然它不是，\NOf course it isn't,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.98,1:01:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但接下来会发生什么是另一本书的故事。\Nbut what happens next\Nis a tale for another book.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.03,1:01:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你为我做的一切，苏菲亚。\NThank you for\Nall you have done, Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.87,1:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了前方的旅程。\NAnd this is for\Nthe journey ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.72,1:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这给我带来了这个。\NWhich brings me to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.06,1:01:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要弄清楚\NI need to figure out
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.86,1:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,用她的魔杖做什么。\Nwhat to do with\Nthe pieces of her wand.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.96,1:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，你可以把他们从悬崖上扔下来。Well, you could just\Ntoss 'em off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.63,1:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想一个更安全的东西。\NI was thinking of\Nsomething a little more secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.90,1:01:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道.你可以…\NI know.\NYou could...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.14,1:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不，这太明显了。\NNo, that's too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.87,1:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.51,1:01:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道.我们可以把它们藏在金库里，\NI know. We can hide them\Nin the treasury,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.64,1:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也不要告诉任何人我们把它。\Nand not tell anyone\Nwhere we put it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.88,1:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对.这将是最好的秘密在艾微。\NYes. It'll be\Nthe best-guarded\Nsecret in Avalor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.52,1:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，内奥米。\NThanks, Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.09,1:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是朋友和大辅导员？\NWhat are friends\Nand Grand Counselors for?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.69,1:02:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我们该不该回去呢？\N( laughs )\NSo, should we\Nhead back down?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.56,1:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你不需要更多的休息吗？\NAre you sure you don't\Nneed more rest?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.33,1:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟，你是57岁。\NYou are 57, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.10,1:02:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.06,1:02:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我的祖母说\NWell, as my{\i1} abuela{\i} says,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.93,1:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,花在魔法珠宝的时间不算。\Ntime spent in magical jewelry\Ndoesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.70,1:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we better go.Then we better go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.94,1:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,王国不会统治自己。\NThe kingdom's\Nnot gonna rule itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.94,1:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,赖特\NRight.

